    "For example, NLP can analyze the complexity of the language used in consent forms and provide suggestions for simplifying the text to match the patient's comprehension.",
    "Furthermore, NLP can be used to generate personalized educational materials tailored to the patient.",
    "ChatbotWhile NLP systems can facilitate conversations between plastic surgeons and patients, they may also conduct their own conversations to provide patients with real-time support and information.",
